metadata.description: The evil Spider-Woman is back with a vengeance, and she wants to take poor little Mattie down bad! It's the knock-down, drag-out slugfest you've been waiting for! Plus: What will happen between Spider-Man and Spider-Woman now that Mattie has learned Peter Parker's secret identity?! And don't miss the disgusting return of Flesh, sans Bones!
metadata.name: Spider-Woman
